             by giving him Mortal Wound with a Pen-knife near the left Pap, on which he lanuguish'd to the 4th of April and then died, he the said 
               <persName id="t17160517-31-person174">
                  Richard 
                  Hathaway 
               <interp inst="t17160517-31-person174" type="surname" value="Hathaway"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17160517-31-person174" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17160517-31-person174" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
